description: KraneShares ICBCUBS S&P China 500 Index UCITS ETF (ticker: CHIN) is a passively managed, index tracking UCITS ETF that seeks to measure the performance of the S&P China 500 Index. The S&P China 500 Index comprises 500 of the largest, most liquid Chinese companies listed on all Chinese stock exchanges, including Mainland China, Hong Kong, and the United States. Companies available for inclusion must be headquartered in China and meet the market capitalization and liquidity minimums required by S&P’s index methodology.
name: KraneShares ICBCUBS S&P China 500 UCITS ETF
